subTitle: Ready for More Tutorials?
definition: There are a few more tutorials ready to walk you through other matters upon request!
bulletListIntro: At the bottom of this workspace:
paragraph1: You may also want to load the Weak-hands Buster V.2 plugin workspace from the tab on the left. It features a tutorial about the Trading Bot Layers to complete your understanding on simulations and how they help you design and debug strategies.
paragraph2: The Trading System Design Tutorials plugin workspace teaches you how to design strategies.
